{"tid":1298139,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[新會員入]連登第一個新手教學po!","createTime":"2019-07-08T19:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T06:35:10.000Z","uid":139605,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"726d6e39cc2c26afdb6353d2e3589d5a67dc3efe","tid":1298139,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:19:50.000Z","msg":"鑑於今晚有會員玩假膠<br />\n而導致有新嚟巴絲同同路人好不幸被fake<br />\n我決定出個新手教學比大家<br />\n等大家容易啲融入連登呢個大家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申定先 我都唔係玩左好耐連登 <br />\n坦白講有啲野我都未明得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以有錯希望大家細力屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋比下意見新會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">終極懶人包:睇連登一定要有獨立思考!千其唔好連登仔講咩信咩!</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n原因一:其實連登有大量三毛<br />\n<br />\n當中仲有三毛好敬業 <br />\n出嘅po好似好有point 但認真諗就會發現唔對路<br />\n例如 尋日有人叫人唔好再扮記者 話會連累記者<br />\n但細心諗下就會發現明明都無人扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又何來&quot;再&quot;呢<br />\n明顯係想屈示威者<br />\n<br />\n又有堆三毛負責comment帶風向<br />\n例如今晚假膠事件發生之後<br />\n有一大堆ac沖出嚟話以後都唔再出嚟<br />\n係咪真係五毛我唔敢講<br />\n但以我認識嘅香港人(仲要講緊呢班人係好有心 願意為香港係夜晚話出嚟就出嚟)係唔似會被人fake一次就以後都唔嚟<br />\n<br />\n至於有無實質方法辨認三毛 我只可以講無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所謂最直觀嘅方法都係睇id no.<br />\n基本上24字頭打後嘅no. 係三毛嘅機會會大少少<br />\n(雖然入得嚟睇嘅巴絲都應該係25 26 打後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n就算係靠前嘅no.都可以係三毛嚟<br />\n所以最實際都係自己思考下<br />\n由言論去判斷係咪三毛<br />\n另外時事台有個三毛list 巴絲信唔過自己可以去跟住嚟block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原因二:連登有假膠<br />\n<br />\n假膠其實都算係連登主要文化嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時係講緊多幾倍假膠<br />\n不過呢個月大家都好認真做正經野先無假膠<br />\n結果一玩膠就玩埋自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而最盞鬼嘅係 每個連登仔都可以係假膠<br />\n就算我呢刻出認真po 我下個po都可以係假膠嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到底 連登仔只係一個代號嚟<br />\n係真實世界到底係邊個人 <br />\n係同路人定三毛 就咁睇個ac係睇唔出<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以以下幾點好重要:<br />\n1.一定要經過自己思考去決定可唔可信!<br />\n2.唔清楚就唔好咁快下定論<br />\nFact check /google左先!<br />\n3.唔好盲目相信正負評!</span><br />\n<br />\n跟住落嚟我會用例子講下幾個連登主要文化<br />\n<br />\n1.假膠<br />\n相信大家經過今晚之後都對假膠有基本嘅認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先 假膠其實有好多種 解密只係其中一個<br />\n除此之外仲有&quot;我公司個90後&quot;系列 &quot;夠500/1000正評就裸跑/派錢etc.&quot;系列<br />\n呢度詳細就唔多講 大家有興趣可以得閒search嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n此外仲有好多 <br />\n近期少少嘅有萎萎撐反送中事件<br />\n#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#in case仲有人唔知 唯唯無反送中 佢重頭到尾都好愛國的 大家唔好咁多幻想<br />\n成件事由頭到尾都無發生過<br />\n但因為多人講 三人成虎 就好多人信<br />\n對呢種無中生有類嘅假膠 (其實所有假膠都係)<br />\n記得獨立思考就可以了<br />\n例子:<br />\nFact:萎萎好耐之前已經北上靠奶共上位<br />\n絕對無可能反送中<br />\nQ.咁點解連登仔話佢反送中?<br />\nA.想搞到萎萎雞毛鴨血 比大陸人罵<br />\n大概係咁<br />\n<br />\n2.曲線<br />\n簡單嚟講即係高級版嘅講反話 <br />\n<br />\n例子:隔離po<br />\n其實白衫好多好克制，係藍衫冇讀過書先咁野蠻<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個po好多人唔明樓主係曲線<br />\n結果就做左真心膠直接負皮上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實呢個樓主係響應緊另一個po<br />\n[推呀]入黎我教你分化班黑警!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1296568\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1296568</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n如果見到非連登主流意見嘅po<br />\n(如支持警察 拉晒示威者坐監 etc.)<br />\n建議望多幾頁先下定論<br />\n一般呢種po好快就會有人/樓主自己忍唔住爆響口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先 希望其他巴絲補充下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9535b3ddbbb8820ccdd9a80c5a943109d6ac5e26","tid":1298139,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:20:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e691f304c31e2cd28f0eba4174fa06c0cf187693","tid":1298139,"uid":139605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:21:46.000Z","msg":"其實本來想直情開個page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奈何樓豬我能力有限<br />\n開住po先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e57150b5c651f405b6dcd638d070dc9fcf5871a","tid":1298139,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:22:05.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"38f82a87a1422c8f3036f885a36d41c8c454c287","tid":1298139,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:22:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d669131df5c4d071bde3c19563c3572bebd42c30","tid":1298139,"uid":253004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:23:03.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b670d350ed30da38e1bdce051721b3973c98ea0","tid":1298139,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f1e65fd3693eda3da7a3e0397492686ca66512","tid":1298139,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0