":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:41:53.000Z","msg":"睡前讀物 入嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「有圖」連儂牆係建制派叫人嚟拆嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298148\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298148</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「運動末來發展」我想分享少少意見同建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295758\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295758</a>"},{"pid":"db4c0d51d6ec17b8f0e0a8622188ebfb47c4e060","tid":1298139,"uid":260878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:47:08.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"96d275af9a9c5c7507fd8112cd60016e1215c16e","tid":1298139,"uid":74198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6d812d454409c0e4db590c95b7c942334b3687","tid":1298139,"uid":9733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}